IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER:

This software is provided for educational and supportive purposes only. It is
NOT a substitute for professional mental health care, diagnosis, or treatment.

If you or someone you know is experiencing a mental health crisis or emergency:
- Call 911 for immediate emergency assistance
- Call or text 988 for the Suicide & Crisis Lifeline
- Text HOME to 741741 for the Crisis Text Line

Always consult with qualified healthcare professionals for medical advice,
diagnosis, and treatment of mental health conditions.
